data-triple-N3.o: "Seven Network (commonly known as Channel Seven or simply Seven) is an Australian commercial television network owned by Seven West Media Limited. It dates back to 4 November 1956, when the first stations on the VHF7 frequency were established in Melbourne, Victoria and Sydney, New South Wales. The Seven Network is one of five main free-to-air networks in Australia."@en
